Package arkanoid.capsule

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Acid
    Acid capsule enables the ball to go through any brick without colliding.
    Break
    Break capsule breaks to the next level.
    Capsule
    Holds common capsule properties.
    Catch
    Catch capsule sticks the ball onto the paddle upon collision and enables the player to relaunch it.
    Disrupt
    Disrupt capsule splits the current ball objects into 3 balls each.
    Expand
    Expand capsule expands the acquiring paddle.
    Fast
    Fast capsule speeds up all balls in the frame.
    Fire
    Fire capsule enables the ball to break multiple hit bricks in one hit.
    Laser
    Laser capsule enables the paddle weaponry.
    Life
    Life capsule increases player's lives by 1.
    Score
    Score capsule increases player score with one of the following values: 50, 100, 250.
    Shrink
    Shrink capsule shrinks the acquiring paddle.
    Slow
    Slow capsule slows down all balls in the frame.
    Vaus
    Vaus capsule adds a new paddle.
